<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
	<HeaderSheet>
		<h1 class="displayHeader">Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p class="bodyPTag">
			OceanBit LLC built the GitShark app as an Open Source Commercial app. This
			SERVICE is provided by OceanBit LLC and is intended for use as is.
		</p>{" "}
		<p class="bodyPTag">
			This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the
			collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided
			to use our Service.
		</p>{" "}
